<h2 id="terms-and-conditions">Terms and conditions</h2>

<p>We‚Äôre a zero cost production. Accordingly, we are not able to pay for contributions/submissions.</p>

<p>What you do get</p>

<p>Your name (role name and real name or pseudonym) will be displayed in the end credits. You can give your role any name you want. If not, we may just add the name as ‚Äúcrewman 1‚Äù, ‚Äúcrewman 2‚Äù and so on‚Ä¶</p>

<p>Video clips will be used in the first episode of TReK‚Äôd, but you may later appear in later episodes if we like your character enough.</p>

<p>By submitting videos to us <strong>you grant us full rights and reuse therein including but not limited to marketing purposes in perpetuity.</strong></p>

